Ever been to a wedding where everyone feels like your cousin? That’s exactly what this day felt like. Every one of Maenusha & Lakshman’s events was packed with laughter, joy, and people who really knew how to show up for each other. People who radiated love. Family by blood and friends who might as well be. 

These are some of my favourite frames that capture just a glimpse of their Catholic ceremony. Trust me, narrowing this down was a mission. I really wanted to include frames from their reception in this set of images, but there were just too many pictures i wanted to post from both events, so i decided that party deserves a post of its own. So watch out next week for those super fun, loud, and chaotic pictures.
